snippet.title: Slender: The Arrival 10 Year Anniversary Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
It's been ten… long… years… but our favourite night stalker has returned. Slender: The Arrival 10 Year Anniversary Update will be launching on Steam, Epic Games Store, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S on October 18, 2023.

Slender: The Arrival 
#SlenderTA
